#CHIP YM2151
#CLOCK 3579545

; YM2151 FM Envelope Test
;
; This test validates envelope behavior of the YM2151 OPM chip
; by playing notes with different durations to observe:
; - Attack (note start)
; - Sustain (note hold)
; - Release (note end)
;
; Test sequence: ascending scale with variable note lengths

#TRACK 0

TEMPO 120

; Short notes (fast attack/release)
c4 . d4 . e4 .

r4

; Medium notes (normal envelope)
c4 - d4 - e4 -

r4

; Long notes (sustained envelope)
f4 _ g4 _ a4 _

r4

; Staccato pattern (short bursts)
c4 . . d4 . . e4 . .

r2

#END
